{{version030}}
{{flavour|Creates a large cloud of noxious fumes, which may cause confusion.}}

'''Noxious cloud''' is a monster-only spell which creates [[Cloud#Noxious fumes|noxious fumes]], identical to the ones created by [[Mephitic Cloud]]. Compared to Mephitic Cloud, this spell's clouds are placed like [[Freezing Cloud]], and the spell is subject to a [[Breath]] timer.

